236 template <class Tx, class Tad>
237 void EulerEquation<Tx, Tad>::calc_dt(const Tx cfl){
238  size_t nic = mesh->nic;
239  size_t njc = mesh->njc;
240  size_t nq = mesh->solution->nq;
241 
242 #pragma omp parallel for
243  for(size_t i=0; i<mesh->nic; i++){
244  for(size_t j=0; j<mesh->njc; j++){
245  Tx rho = mesh->solution->q[i][j][0];
246  Tx u = mesh->solution->q[i][j][1]/rho;
247  Tx v = mesh->solution->q[i][j][2]/rho;
248  Tx rhoE = mesh->solution->q[i][j][3];
249  Tx p = (rhoE - 0.5*rho*(u*u + v*v))*(GAMMA-1.0);
250  Tx lambda = sqrt(GAMMA*p/rho) + fabs(u) + fabs(v);
251  Tx len_min = std::min(mesh->ds_eta[i][j], mesh->ds_chi[i][j]);
252  Tx mu = config->freestream->mu_inf;
253  for(size_t k=0; k<nq; k++)
254  mesh->solution->dt[i][j][k] = cfl/(lambda/len_min + 2.0*mu/len_min/len_min);
255  //dt[i][j][4] = dt[i][j][0];
256  }
257  }
258 
259 }

261 template <class Tx, class Tad>
262 void EulerEquation<Tx, Tad>::initialize(){
263  size_t nic = mesh->nic;
264  size_t njc = mesh->njc;
265 
266  for(size_t i=0; i<nic; i++){
267  for(size_t j=0; j<njc; j++){
268  auto rho_inf = config->freestream->rho_inf;
269  auto u_inf = config->freestream->u_inf;
270  auto v_inf = config->freestream->v_inf;
271  auto p_inf = config->freestream->p_inf;
272  mesh->solution->q[i][j][0] = rho_inf;
273  mesh->solution->q[i][j][1] = rho_inf*u_inf;
274  mesh->solution->q[i][j][2] = rho_inf*v_inf;
275  mesh->solution->q[i][j][3] = p_inf/(GAMMA-1.0) + 0.5*rho_inf*(u_inf*u_inf + v_inf*v_inf);
276  }
277  }
278  if(config->io->restart){
279  mesh->iomanager->read_restart();
280  }
281  size_t nq = mesh->solution->nq;
282  size_t ntrans = mesh->solution->ntrans;
283  for(size_t i=0; i<nic; i++){
284  for(size_t j=0; j<njc; j++){
285  for(size_t k=0; k<nq+ntrans; k++){
286  mesh->solution->q_tmp[i][j][k] = mesh->solution->q[i][j][k];
287  }
288  }
289  }
290 
291 }
